\ip Aisaia kamagh…®n m…®gei, Judaba uan gumazir ekiaba ko, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n apengan ik…®va, arazir aghuibara g…®nt…®gh. Egh me kamagh…®n damu, me derav…®ra ikiam. Me arazir kurar kabar g…®nt…®ghv…®ra ik…®t…®, God me gas…®ghas…®gham. 
\ip Egha Aisaia uaghan g…®n otivamin dughiar aghuim…®n akam akuri. Atrivim Devit…®n ovavir borir mam, an atrivim…®n otoght…®, nguibar av…®ribar gumazamiziba, bar dughiar aghuim iniam. 
\ip 2. Sapta 40--55. Ak…®nafarim…®n akuar kam…®n, a Judaba Babilon…®n kalabus…®n ikiamin dughiam…®n gun m…®gei. Bizir kaba, da ak…®nafarir akuar faragha itim…®n itir bizibar g…®n otifi. Judaba naviba osemegha itima, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim, dughiar aghuim otoght…®ma, me bar akueghamin dughiam…®n gun me m…®gei. God a biziba bar dar afeziam. A ghaze, Judabar apaniba me inigh mang…®t…®, me bar uan nguibam…®n saghon ikiam, eght…® God me g…®namadaghan kogham. A fom…®ra me gamizir akar d…®k…®r…®zibagh n…®ghn…®ghav…®ra iti. Egh a Persian Atrivim Sairus am…®seveght…®ma, a uan ingangarim damuva, Judaba amadaght…®, me uamategh uan nguibamra izam. Egha God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim uaghan kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, Israelian agharim…®n, God nguazir kam…®n gumazamiziba bar derav…®ra me damuam. 
\ip Ak…®nafarim…®n akuar kam…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®ar av…®rir maba uaghan kamagh…®n iti, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ingangarir gumazir mam otogh, m…®zazim inigh, egh gumazamizibar akuragham. Krais…®n g…®n zuir gumazamizir av…®riba kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim iti, kar Iesusra. 
\ip 3. Sapta 56--66. Ak…®nafarim…®n akuar kam, Judaba uamategha iza Jerusalem…®n itima, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim, akam me gan…®di. Ak…®nafarir kam…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®ar maba kamagh…®n m…®gei, God uan akar d…®k…®r…®zim g…®n…®ghn…®ghav…®ra iti, ez…® bizir kam, gavgavim Judabar navibagh an…®di. Ez…® ak…®nafarir kam…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®ar otevir maba kamagh…®n me m…®gei, Me God…®n apengan ik…®va, an ziam fer arazir aghuibar g…®nt…®gh…®va, God…®n ziam f…®va, an amamangar…®gh…®va, egh ofaba a dan…®ng. Me uaghan gumazamizir biziba puvat…®zibagh n…®ghn…®gh, men akurvagh. 
\ip Akar aghuir mam, Aisaia 61:1-2…®n iti, Iesus uan ingangarim foregh a damuamin dughiam…®n, an a d…®borima, gumazamiziba a barakis. (N…® Luk 4:16-21…®n gan.) 
