\v 5 \x - \xo 6:5 \xt Gumazir Dapaniba 6:22; 13:22; Jeremaia 1:6\x*Ez…® k…® atiatigha ghaze, ‚ÄúMaia, k…® ikuvigha g…®fa. Nan m…®zem zurara akar kurabav g…®av…®ra iti, ez…® k…® gumazamizir m…®zer akar kurabav geiba ko iti. K…® arazir kurabagh amir gumazim, egha dat…®r…®gh…®n k…® Atrivim…®n ganigha g…®fa, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim. K…® uan damazimning…®n an ganigha g…®fa, kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® aremegham.‚Äù 
