\v 1 \x - \xo 7:1 \xt 2 Atriviba 16:5; 2 Eghaghaniba 28:5-6\x*Dughiar kam, Usian otarim Jotam, ez…® Jotam Ahas…®n afeziam. Ez…® Ahas Jerusalem…®n aven, Judan atrivim…®n itima, m…®dorozim oto. Resin, a Sirian atrivim, ez…® Remalian otarim Peka, a Israelian atrivim, aning ghua Jerusalemia ko m…®sosi. Egha aning a inian iburaghburaki. 
