\v 6 Me kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, me iz…® kantri Judan gumazamiziba ko m…®sogh atiatim an gumazamizibar an…®ng, ua bagh kantri inigh, egh Tabel…®n otarim am…®seveght…® an atrivim…®n ikiam.\f + \fr 7:6 \ft E gumazir kam…®n ziam g…®fozir puvat…®, me kamagh…®n a d…®bori ‚ÄúTabel…®n otarim.‚Äù Fofozir gumaziba kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, a Sirian adarazir gumazir mam.\f* 
