\v 14 \x - \xo 7:14 \xt Aisaia 9:6; Matyu 1:23; Luk 1:31; 1:34\x*Kamagh…®n, Ekiam uab…® ababanir tam n…®n akagham. Ababanir kam kamak…®n. Amizir gumazitam ko akuizir puvat…®zim navim asegh, otaritam bategham. Eght…® me ziar kam Emanuel a dar…®gham.‚Äù\f + \fr 7:14 \ft Hibrun akam…®n, ziam Emanuel, an m…®ngarim kamagh…®n ghu, ‚ÄúGod e ko iti.‚Äù\f* 
\p  
\v 15 ‚ÄúEght…® an aghung mang…® egh biziba tuis…®ghamin n…®ghn…®zim ik…® suam, bizir manam a dera an a damuam, ez…® bizir manam a ikufi, an a damuan kogham. Egh dughiar kam…®n, a hani ko sis amam, daghem sis, me bulmakau ko sipsip…®n oter eborim…®n dar ingari.\f + \fr 7:15 \ft Israelia gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n ikiav…®ra itir dughiam…®n, me dagher av…®riba puvat…®. Egha me kamagh…®n oraki, Kenan…®n nguazim haniba ko oter eborir av…®riba iti, egha me ghaze kar dagher bar aghuibara. N…® Ua Me Ini 3:8…®n gan. Egha me g…®n iza Kenan…®n nguazim…®n otivigha garima, hani ko oter eborim, aningra itir puvat…®, dagher guar av…®riba uaghan iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazir maba kamagh n…®ghn…®si, gumazir maba ghaze, borir kam dagher aghuibara damam, mati hani ko sis. Ez…® gumazir maba ghaze, akar kam…®n m…®ngarim bar igharav…®ra iti. Me ghaze, azeniba bar dar dagheba bar ikuvigham. (N…® ves 21-25…®n gan.) Ez…® dagher guar pumuning iti, hani ko oter eborir damamim o daghem sis, me oter eborim…®n an ingari.\f* 
\p  
\v 16 ‚ÄúO Atrivim Ahas, n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n atrivir kamning…®n atiati. Eght…® aning…®n kantrining bar ikuvigham, eght…® aning…®n nguazimning pura ikiam. Dughiar kam…®n borir kam, arazir manam a dera an a damuam, ez…® arazir manam a ikufi, an a damuan kogham. Egh a t…®ghar dagh foghamin dughiam…®n bizir kaba otivam.  
\v 17 Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God n…® ko n…®n gumazamiziba ko n…®n adarazi bagh dughiar bar kuram amadaght…® a izam. Dughiar Judaba ko Israelia uari abigha ikia iza dat…®r…®gh…®n, os…®mt…®zir tam me batozir puvat…®. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n os…®mt…®zir bar kuram me bativam. Os…®mt…®zir kam a kamak…®n: Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Asirian atrivim…®n amamangat…®ght…®, a Judaba bagh izam. 
\p  
\v 18 ‚ÄúEght…® dughiar kam…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God bobem…®n Isipian diaght…®ma, m…®dorozir gumazir bar av…®rim, saghon mar Isip…®n Faneba bar dar suiabar ikegh, berezir b…®zir bar av…®rim…®n m…®n izam. Egh an Asiriaba bobem…®n men diaght…® me aparir okoruabar m…®n izam.  
\v 19 Egh me kantri Judan danganiba bar dagh iz…®vagham. Me danganir moziba bar dagh iz…®vagh, dag…®ar toriba ko ogheba aghuir danganiba ko benir d…®koniba itiba bar dagh iz…®vagham. 
\p  
\v 20 ‚ÄúDughiar kam…®n, Ekiam Yufretis…®n Fanem…®n vong…®n Asirian atrivim inigham. An Ekiam…®n resan m…®n otogh, egh ia Judaba, a ian dapanar…®zibagh isam. A ian ghuamas…®zibagh is…®va, ian dapaniba ko m…®karzir ar…®ziba sara isam. 
\p  
\v 21 ‚ÄúEght…® dughiar kam…®n, apaniba iz…® ian bulmakauba ko sipsipbav sogham. Eght…® gumazitam bulmakaun vam…®ra ko sipsip…®n pumuningra ik…®t…®,  
\v 22 da oter eborir av…®ribar amut…® da otivam. Eght…® an oter eborir kam inigh damamin sis…®n ingaram. Eght…® gumazamizir ikiav…®ra itir varazira, me haniba ko sisbar amam. 
\p  
\v 23-24 ‚ÄúDughiar kam…®n ian azeniba bar mogh…®ra ikuvigham. Dat…®r…®gh…®n wain…®n azeniba da wain…®n ikar…®zir 1,000pla iti, ez…® azeniba vaghvagha dar ivezim 1,000 kina. Eght…® g…®n temer ataghatariba itiba ko benir kuraba otivigh azenir kaba avegham. Eght…® gumaziba danganir kabar as…®ziba buris…®, me uan barir piba sara mangam.  
\v 25 Dat…®r…®gh…®n gumazamiziba m…®ghs…®ar dozibar dagheba opari. Eght…® g…®n temer ataghatariba itiba ko benir kuraba otivigh m…®ghs…®ar dozir kaba bar, da avegham. Gumazamiziba d…®konibar atiating egh me uam mang…® azenibar ingaran kogham. Puvat…®. Me pura bulmakauba ko sipsipba ateght…®, darara danganir kabar daru dagheba buriam.‚Äù 
\c 8  
\s1 Asiriaba m…®soghs…® iz…® Damaskus ko Samarian bizir aghuiba okemegham 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n na m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® os…®rs…® bizir ekiatam inigh, egh a gis…®n en akam…®n letan k…®nir kabar, ziar kam osirigh, ‚ÄòMe Zuam…®ram Okemegh Zuam…®ram a Inigh Mang…®.‚Äô N…® bar derav…®ram an osirigh, eght…® gumazamiziba derav…®ram an gan…®va a d…®ponam.\f + \fr 8:1 \ft Hibrun akam bizitam…®n m…®ngarim deragha bigha m…®kemezir puvat…®.\f* 
\v 2 Egh akar n…® osiramin kam gavgavim a dan…®ng…®s…®, n…® gumazir aghuir kamning inigh, ofa gamir gumazim Uria ko Jeberekian otarim Sekaraia, aning gant…®, n…® an osir.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 3 Ez…® k…® g…®n ghua uan amuim, a God…®n akam inigha izir amizir mam, a koma akui. Ez…® a navim asegha otarim bate. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n na m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® ziar kam a dat…®gh, ‚ÄòMe Zuam…®ram Okemegh Zuam…®ram A Inigh Mang…®.‚Äô\f + \fr 8:3 \ft Gumazir maba ghaze, akam inigha izir gumazim Asaia, an amuim uaghan akam inigha izir amizir mam.\f* 
\v 4 Borir kam t…®ghar kamagh…®n fogh suam, kar nan amebam ko nan Afeziam, ez…® dughiar kamra, Asirian kantrin m…®dorozir gumaziba iz…® Damaskus…®n nguibar ekiam ko Samarian nguibar ekiam…®n bizir aghuiba okemegh, mang…® uan atrivim dan…®ngam. Ez…® borir kam…®n ziam…®n m…®ngarim kamak…®n, Zuam…®ram Okemegh Zuam…®ram A Inigh Mang…®.‚Äù 
\s1 Asirian atrivim Judaba d…®kab…®nasava ami, ez…® God me ko iti 
\p  
\v 5 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua kamagh…®n na m…®gei: 
\b  
\q1  
\v 6 ‚ÄúK…® Ekiam, k…® Jerusalem…®n borogh…®n itir d…®pam Siloan m…®n iti, 
\q2 egha zurara aghumra ivemari. 
\q1 Ez…® Judan gumazamiziba kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, K…® ti gavgaviba puvat…®. 
\q2 Egha me Atrivim Resin…®n gavgavim ko Israel…®n atrivir kam…®n gavgavim g…®n…®ghn…®gha, 
\q3 atiatir bar ekiam men itima, agorogem me m…®sozima aghariba men am…®ra. 
\q1  
\v 7-8 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® Ekiam, k…® Yufretis…®n Fanem damight…®, 
\q2 an aperiam bar ekevegh danganiba bar da avaragham. 
\q1 D…®pam nguibaba bar da avaragh, Yufretis…®n Fanem…®n m…®riam…®n ikegh iz…® 
\q2 kantri Judan otogham, 
\q3 egh d…®pam bar buigh iz…®v anang gumazim…®n f…®ragharim…®n tugham. 
\q1 Yufretis…®n Fanem, an Asirian kantrin atrivir gavgavim uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko men nedazim. 
\q2 Ez…® e fo, God e ko iti! 
\q1 Egha derav…®ra e geghuvam, 
\q2 mati kuarazir av…®zir bar ekiamning itim, an aning onegha m…®gha ghua 
\q3 en nguazim bar, derav…®ra an gari.‚Äù\f + \fr 8:7-8 \ft Hibrun akam…®n ziam Emanuel kamagh…®n ghu, ‚ÄúGod e ko iti.‚Äù Aisaia 7:14…®n aven, Aisaia ghaze, boritam otoght…® me ziam Emanuel a dar…®gham. Aisaia ti borir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, ‚ÄúEmanuel.‚Äù\f* 
\b  
\q1  
\v 9 Ia derav…®ram oragh, ia kantrin rogh…®ra itiba ko saghon itibar gumazamiziba. 
\q2 Ia uari akuvagh m…®soghs…® gan ik…®. 
\q1 Eght…® ian gavgavim bighir…®ght…®, 
\q2 ia d…®gavir kuram damigh puram onganim damuam. 
\q1  
\v 10 God e ko iti. 
\q2 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, bizir ia damuasa n…®ghn…®zim, 
\q3 ia a damut…®, ian tuavim p…®right…®, bizir kam otoghan kogham. 
\q1 Ia bizir av…®ribav m…®k…®mam, 
\q2 eght…® dar dagheba puvat…®gham.\f + \fr 8:10 \ft Hibrun akar kam Emanuel a kamak…®n, ‚ÄúGod e ko iti,‚Äù a ziar kam ko magh ghu Emanuel. N…® Aisaia 7:13-15 ko 8:7-8…®n gan.\f* 
\s1 Aisaia uan adarazi ko me Godram atiating 
\p  
\v 11 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n gavgavim barazima, a nan anadima, a kamagh…®n na m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® gumazamizir kabar n…®ghn…®ziba ko arazibar g…®n mangan mark…®.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 8:12-13 \xt 1 Pita 3:14-15\x*Gumazamiziba kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, gumazir maba kantri Juda gas…®ghas…®ghasa akam ak…®ri, eght…® n…® uan adarazi ko kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®, akar kam a guizbang…®ra. Bar puvat…®. Egh gumazamiziba puv…®ram atiating n…®ghamin dughiam…®n, ia men m…®n puv…®rama atiatingan mark…®.  
\v 13 Ia kamagh…®n fogh suam, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgavim Bar Itim, a God…®n Bar Zuezim, egha arazir aghuibara ami. Ia anar…®ram atiating…®va an apengan ik…®.  
\v 14-15 \x - \xo 8:14-15 \xt 1 Pita 2:8\x*A gumazamizibar mogomer danganir bar gavgavim…®n m…®n iti. Egha a dag…®am…®n m…®n Israelia ko Judan gumazamiziba aruir tuavim…®n iti. Eght…® men av…®riba uan dagariba as…® daghir…® ikuvigham. Ez…® Jerusalem…®n gumazamiziba, an azuazim…®n m…®n men suighasa iti. Eght…® men av…®riba azuazir kam…®n guam. Jerusalem…®n gumazamiziba, k…® guizbang…®ra azuazim…®n m…®n men suighasa iti.‚Äù 
\s1 Ekiam damuasa m…®kemezir biziba, Aisaia dar m…®zua iti 
\q1  
\v 16 Nan suren gumazibar damazim…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God na gan…®ngizir akar kaba, 
\q2 k…® da osirigh, da righ…®va da ikegh kandel…®n gris…®n anem…®gh…®r…®gh, 
\q3 uan ababanim is…® kandel…®n gris dat…®ght…®, da deraghv…®ra ikiam.\f + \fr 8:16 \ft Aisaia akam osirigha ghaze, Gumazamiziba God…®n akabar g…®n mangan koght…®, God ghaze a bizir kabar amut…® da otivam. Egha Aisaia akar kabar ak…®nafarim righa, a savsuigha, kandel…®n gris isa tong…®ram a gat…®, egha a uan ababanim isa kandel…®n gris gis…®n at…®, eght…® gumazitam an akaba angaran kogham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, bizir kaba g…®n otivight…®, gumazamiziba an ak…®nafarir akar ir…®ghizir kam kuigh akar an osiriziba d…®pon kamagh…®n guiz…®n fogh suam, Aisaian akaba, da guizbang…®ra.\f* 
\q1  
\v 17 \x - \xo 8:17 \xt Hibru 2:13\x*Egh k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God damuasa m…®kemezir biziba, 
\q2 k…® puram a m…®zuam da bagh gan ikiam. 
\q1 K…® fo, an ak…®rim ragha Israelian gumazamizibagh asagha g…®fa, 
\q2 egh a ua ragh men ganan kogham. 
\q3 Eght…® k…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an ik…®v…®ra ikiam. 
\b  
\p  
\v 18 \x - \xo 8:18 \xt Hibru 2:13\x*Ia gan. Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, Saion…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n ikiava, borir kaba na gan…®ngi. Ez…® k…® uan boriba ko an e at…®z…® e Israelian gumazamiziba bagha, ababanim…®n m…®n iti. Eght…® me en gan…®va, God…®n Arazibagh n…®ghn…®gham.\f + \fr 8:18 \ft Aisaia God…®n akam akunigha g…®fa. A dat…®r…®gh…®n aghumra ik…® gant…®, God damuasa ifongezir bizibar amuam. Eght…® gumazamiziba Aisaian gan…®va egh an boribar ziabar m…®ngaribagh n…®ghnigh…®va, a me m…®kemezir akabagh n…®ghn…®gham. N…® Aisaian boribar izibar m…®ngaribagh fofoghs…®, n…® Aisaia 7:3 ko 8:3-4…®n gan. Ves 17-18…®n akar kam, ‚ÄúIsrael…®n gumazamiziba,‚Äù a kantri Israel ko kantri Judan gumazamizibav gei.\f* 
\s1 Godra uan gumazamiziba bizir aghuiba me gan…®di 
\p  
\v 19 Eght…® gumazamiziba ia m…®k…®mt…®, ia mang…® gumazamizir oveaghuezibar duaba ko m…®k…®m, me da n…®ghn…®ziba iniam. Egha me kuarazibar m…®n imoba, sighsirir akabar m…®gei. Ez…® gumazamizir oveaghueziba, me n…®ghn…®ziba gumazamizir angam…®ra itibar an…®ngan iburagham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e tizim bagh aseba ko gumazamizir oveaghueziba da n…®ghn…®ziba iniasa ivemara me bagha zui? Puvat…®. Arazir kam ikufi. Me uan God bagh mang…®.  
\v 20 Me God…®n Araziba ko an Akar Gavgaviba ko, an n…®ghn…®zim g…®fogh. Egh me kamagh…®n damighan kogh, me m…®tarmem…®n averara ik…®t…®, am…®nim me bagh tiraghan kogham, eght…® me dughiar aghuitam…®n ganighan kogham.\f + \fr 8:20 \ft Ves 19 ko 20…®n, Hibrun akam deragha m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f* 
\v 21 Puvat…®. Me bar dughiar kuram iniam. Me navir os…®mt…®zir dafaba ik…®t…®, m…®tiriaba men agh…®t…®, me pura tintinibar kantrin aven daruam. M…®tiriam me damut…® me atar, akar kurabar uan aseba ko atrivim m…®k…®mam. Me kogh overiam…®n gan…®va,  
\v 22 v…®n nguazim…®n gan, egh me bar bizir aghuitam…®n ganighan kogham. Bar puvat…®. Me os…®mt…®ziba ko dughiar kuramra danganiba bar da gan ikiam, mati am…®nirb…®rim bar me avara. Egh me os…®mt…®zim gitav…®ragh ar…®mangamin tuaviba puvat…®gham. 
\c 9  
\s1 God…®n, gumazamiziba bar akueghs…®, an atrivir aghuim me dan…®ngam 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 9:1 \xt Matyu 4:15\x*Eght…® g…®n, os…®mt…®ziba aterir darasi, me uam osemeghan kogham. Ia fo, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, fom…®ra Naptali ko Sebulun…®n anababar nguibaba bar dagh as…®ghas…®ghiz…®, me bar aghums…®ki. Eght…® g…®n dughiatam iz…®t…®, tuavir ongarim…®n zuim…®n borogh…®ra itir danganim, ko Jordan…®n Fanem…®n dadarir vong…®n itir danganim, a Galilin Distrigh…®n nguazim, danganir kam Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamizir av…®riba uaghan an aven iti, nguibar kaba uaghan bar mogh…®ra, men dughiar kuraba da g…®vaght…®, me ziar ekiam iniam.\f + \fr 9:1 \ft Asiriaba izava kantri Israel…®n m…®sogha, Sebulun ko Naptalin anababar nguibaba ko nguibar igharaziba ko Galilin Distrigh…®n not…®n amadaghan itir nguaziba ini. N…® 2 Atriviba 15:29…®n gan. Kantrin kam…®n danganir kam, an ziar mam Galili.\f* 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 \x - \xo 9:2 \xt Matyu 4:16; Luk 1:79; Efesus 5:8; 5:14\x*Gumazamizir arazir kurabar m…®tatem…®n aven aruiba, 
\q2 me dat…®r…®gh…®n angazangarir ekiam…®n gari. 
\q1 Me danganir m…®tatem…®n apiaghav ikiava aremeghasava ami, 
\q2 ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n am…®nim tiraz…® angazangarim me gisira. 
\q1  
\v 3 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…® uan gumazamizibagh amiz…®ma, me bar av…®raseme, 
\q2 N…® me gamiz…®, me bar akonge. 
\q1 Me n…®n damazim…®n bar akongezir arazir kam, 
\q2 mati me azenibar dagheba asia da bagha bar akonge. 
\q2 Egha mati m…®dorozir gumaziba m…®dorozim gamigha g…®vagha, 
\q3 bizir me iniziba da tuiragha uari gan…®ga bar akonge. 
\q1  
\v 4 Gumazamiziba bar akongezir bizim, a kamak…®n: 
\q2 N…® fom…®ra Midian…®n kantrin gavgaviba ap…®raghar…®ghiz…® mogh…®n, 
\q3 dat…®r…®gh…®n men apanibar gavgaviba ap…®ragharigha g…®fa. 
\q1 Guizbang…®ra, apaniba faragha n…®n gumazamizibagh ativagha, 
\q2 me gamima, me mati bulmakaun mam, gumazim ter ararim isa an tuem gat…®gha, 
\q3 ingangarim zuam…®ram a damuasa, a gaghora a m…®sosi. 
\q1 Ez…® n…® apanibar aghoriba ko ter arariba ap…®raghar…®ghiz…®, 
\q2 me ua n…®n gumazamiziba paza me gamir puvat…®.\f + \fr 9:4 \ft Fom…®ra Midiania paza Israelia gami, ez…® Gideon…®n dafarim…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God men gavgaviba ap…®ri. N…® Gumazir Dapaniba 6:1-6 ko 7:9-25…®n gan.\f* 
\q1  
\v 5 Guizbang…®ra, m…®dorozir gumaziba m…®dorozir korotiar aghua ghua m…®soziba, 
\q2 avim bar dar isigham. 
\q1 Men dagarir asuaba ko men korotiar gumazibar ghuziba itiba, 
\q2 avim bar adar isigham. 
\q1 Eght…® os…®mt…®ziba bar g…®vaght…®ma, 
\q2 dughiar aghuim otogham. 
\q1  
\v 6 \x - \xo 9:6 \xt Aisaia 7:14; Luk 2:11; Jon 3:16; Taitus 2:13\x*Bar guizbang…®ra, otarir mam amebam e bagha a bate, 
\q2 a borir God e gan…®ngizir mam. 
\q1 Eght…® an e gativagh en ganamin arazir kam, 
\q2 mati gumazim d…®penir ak…®nir dafam uan d…®p…®zim gat…®gha aneteri. 
\q1 Kar an ziaba, 
\q2 Gumazir N…®ghn…®zir Bar Aghuiba An…®dim, 
\q2 ko God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, 
\q2 ko Afeziar Zurara Ikiav…®ra Itim, 
\q2 ko Atrivir Dabirabir Aghuim ko Navir Am…®rizim An…®dim. 
\q1  
\v 7 \x - \xo 9:7 \xt 2 Atriviba 19:31; Daniel 2:44; Luk 1:32-33\x*Eght…® atrivir kam, Atrivim Devit…®n danganim inigh, 
\q2 Devit…®n atrivir dabirabim daperagh gumazamizibar ganam. 
\q1 Eght…® a gumazamizibagh ativagh men ganamin gavgavir kam, 
\q2 an ek…®v mang…®v…®ra ikiam. 
\q1 Kamagh…®n m…®doroziba ua puvat…®ght…®, 
\q2 gumazamiziba navir am…®rizim…®n ikia, deraghv…®ra dapiagh ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam. 
\q1 Atrivir kam, guiz…®n arazim…®n g…®n ghua biziba deragha da tuis…®gha, 
\q2 God…®n arazir aghuibara amuasav…®ra iti. 
\q1 A kamagh…®n damut…®, 
\q2 an atrivir ingangarim dat…®r…®gh…®n ikegh gavgavigh mang…®v…®ra ikiam. 
\q1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, uan gumazamiziba guizbang…®ra bar me gifonge, 
\q2 kamagh…®n amiz…®, a bizir kam damight…® an otogham. 
\s1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God Israelia gas…®ghas…®ki 
\q1  
\v 8 Ekiam m…®kemegha g…®vagha ghaze, 
\q2 a kantri Israel gas…®ghas…®gham, kar Jekop…®n ovavir boriba. 
\q1 Eght…® dughiar kurar kam me batoght…®, 
\q1  
\v 9 Samarian nguibar ekiam…®n itir gumazamiziba ko, Efraim…®n adarasi, 
\q2 me bar kamagh…®n fogh suam, Ekiamra bizir kam…®n me gami. 
\q1 Egha me dat…®r…®gh…®n ghaze, me bar p…®n mar iti, 
\q2 egha uarira uan ziaba fe. 
\q1 Me kamagh…®n m…®gei, 
\q1  
\v 10 ‚ÄúApaniba en brigh…®n d…®peniba akaragharigha, en temer fikba okaghar…®ki. 
