\q1 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia kantri Elam…®n itir m…®dorozir gumaziba, 
\q2 ia iz…® Babilonia m…®sogh. 
\q1 Eght…® ia Midian kantrin m…®dorozir gumaziba, 
\q2 ia iz…® nguibar ekiar kam an ek…®arugh. 
\q1 K…® os…®mt…®zir Babilonia gumazamizir igharazibagh an…®diba ag…®vagham.‚Äù 
