\q1 Idomian kantrin itir gumaziba d…®a kamagh…®n azangs…®si, 
\q2 ‚ÄúO apaniba bagha garir gumazim, d…®magarim manad…®zogh…®n g…®vagham? 
\q2 A bar guizbang…®ra, dughiar manam…®n g…®vagham?‚Äù\f + \fr 21:11 \ft Hibrun akam, ves 11 ko 13, aning…®n m…®ngarim bigha m…®kemezir puvat…®. Gumazir maba ghaze, Duman nguibar ekiam, a Arebian nguibar ekiar mam. Jenesis, sapta 25:13-15, ziar kam Duma, a ziam Tema ko Kedar ko iti. (N…® saptan kam…®n ves 14-16…®n gan.) Ez…® ves 11 uaghan kantri Idom…®n m…®gei. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazir maba ghaze, vez…®n kam…®n ziam Duma a kantri Idom.\f* 
