\p  
\v 16 Ez…® Ekiam kamagh…®n na m…®keme, ‚ÄúKedar…®n nguibar ekiam…®n itir gumazamiziba, uan bizir aghuiba sara bar g…®vaghamin azenir bar vam…®ra iti. K…® bar derav…®ra azenir kam…®n dughiaba vaghvagha da medi, egh azenir kam g…®vamin aruer kamra, k…® me damuasa m…®kemezir bizibar me damuam.  
\v 17 Kedaria, me m…®dorozir gumazir bar gavgaviba, egha me pibar m…®soghan bar fo. Egh me bar g…®vaght…®, m…®dorozir gumazir buangningra ikiam. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian God, k…® m…®kemegha g…®fa.‚Äù 
\c 22  
\s1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Jerusalem…®n gumazamizibar atari 
