\q2 me m…®dorozir gumazir gavgavibar m…®n m…®soghava ariaghirezir puvat…®.\f + \fr 22:1-2 \ft Asiriaba iza Jerusalem ek…®aruzir dughiam…®n, Jerusalem…®n gumaziba Asiriabar atiatigha tuivigha gavgavigha me ko m…®soghezir puvat…®. Jerusalem…®n gumazir maba arasava ami, ez…® Asiriaba men suigha me m…®soghez…® me ariaghire. Ez…® marazi nguibar ekiam…®n aven ikia ar…®mariaba ko m…®tiriam bang…®n ariaghire.\f* 
