\v 19 ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God ingangarim…®n n…® ag…®vagh n…® batueght…®, n…® pura ik…®va ua ziaba puvat…®gham.  
\v 20 Bizir kam otoght…®, k…® uan ingangarir gumazim Eliakim…®n diaght…® a izam. A Hilkian otarim.  
\v 21 Eght…® k…® korotiar ruarir kam is…® Eliakim darugh, m…®ter atrivim…®n ingangarir gumazim uan ivariam gitim a gikegh, n…® amir ingangarim…®n gavgavim inigh an dafarim dat…®gham. Eght…® an afeziam…®n m…®n otogh bar mogh…®ra Jerusalem nguibam…®n gumazamiziba, ko Judian nguibaba bar me gativagh men ganam.  
\v 22 \x - \xo 22:22 \xt Akar Mogomem 3:7\x*Eght…® k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® Atrivim Devit…®n d…®penim…®n kiba is…®, an dafarim dat…®gham. Eght…® a tiam kuight…® tav a dukuaghan kogham. A tiam dukuaght…® tav a kuighan kogham.  
\v 23 K…® a damight…®, a ingangarir kam bagh bar gavgavigham, mati purirpenibar suizir afughafuziba, da purirpenim…®n suiraz…® a danganir vam…®ra ikia gavgafi. Eght…® an adarazi bar mogh…®ra ingangarir an amir kam bang…®n ziar ekiam iniam. 
\p  
\v 24 ‚ÄúEght…® an adarazi ko an boriba ko namakaba, me bar mogh…®ra an guigh…®v ik…®, uarir akurvaghs…® an azangs…®gham. Me, m…®neba ko m…®tariba akezir mam…®n guraghav iti mogh…®n, me an guigh…®v ikiam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 25 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúDughiar kam…®n akezir kam, a faragha gavgavigha iti, egh a dat…®r…®gh…®n asighir…®gh ir…®gham. Eght…® bizir an guighav ikia os…®mt…®zim a gan…®diba, me bar ikuvigham. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, k…® m…®kemegha g…®fa.‚Äù 
\c 23  
