\c 36  
\ms1 Asiriaba Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam iniasa 
\mr (Sapta 36--39) 
\s1 Asiriaba Jerusalem iniasava ami 
\r (2 Atriviba 18:13-37; 2 Eghaghaniba 32:1-19) 
\p  
\v 1 Hesekia 14plan azenibar an atrivim…®n itima, ez…® Asirian Atrivim Senakerip, uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko iza Judaba ko m…®sogha, me ab…®ragha men nguibar ekiar d…®vazir gavgaviba av…®niziba bar da ini. Egha me Jerusalem inizir puvat…®.  
\v 2 Senakerip, Lakis…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ikia uan abuir gumazim ko m…®dorozir gumazir b…®zir dafam amadaz…®, me Lakis ategha, Atrivim Hesekia bagha Jerusalem…®n zui. Me an borogh…®n ghua otifi. Dughiar kam…®n, danganir mam iti, Mozir D…®par P…®n Itim…®n daghurim, d…®pam an ghuaghira Jerusalem…®n otifi. Daghurir kam, a tuavir ekiar ghua iniba ruer danganim…®n borogh…®n iti. Asiriaba otivigha danganir kam…®n tuivighav iti. 
\p  
\v 3 Ez…® Israel…®n gumazir dapanir 3pla ghuav a bato. Kar, Hilkian otarim Eliakim, an atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n garir gumazim, ko Sepna, atrivim…®n ak…®nafariba osirir gumazim, ko Asap…®n otarim Joa, an atrivim amir bizibar eghaghaniba bar a da osirir gumazim, me zui.  
\v 4 Ez…® 3plan gumazir kaba ghuava Asirian abuir gumazir kam batoz…®, an akar gavgavim…®n me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa mang…®, Asirian atrivir ekiam…®n akar gavgavir kam Hesekia m…®kemegh. A kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòHesekia, n…® gavgavir manam ikia egha nan apengan ikian aghua?  
\v 5 M…®g…®r…®g…®ar k…®niba ti m…®dorozim…®n gavgavim gafiraz, o? Bar puvat…®! N…® nan akaba barazir puvat…®. Egha n…® ghaze, tina iz…® n…®n akuragham! Ez…® n…® na baraghan aghua.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 36:6 \xt Esekiel 29:6-7\x*K…® fo, kantri Isip n…®n akuragh m…®soghasa, n…® a bagha gara m…®zua iti. Egha k…® n…® m…®gei, Isip mati abuar m…®siam d…®p…®riaghir…®gha g…®fa. Egh n…® a inigh fidizim…®n m…®n an suiragh darut…®, an ruaghatevim n…®n agharim m…®t…®gham. Isip…®n atrivim…®n arazim abuar m…®siar kam…®n m…®rara ghu. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, m…®soghamin dughiam…®n a iz…® n…®n akuraghan kogham.  
\v 7 Egh n…® ti kamagh…®n m…®k…®mam, ia Israelia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n iti, a ian God, a ian akuragham. Ez…® k…® ghaze, bar puvat…®gham. E fo, Hesekia, n…® uab…® ghua, m…®ghs…®abar p…®n itir danganir an ziam feba ko, an ofa gamir dakozir pura tintinibar itiba bar dagh as…®ghas…®ki. Egha n…® Judaba ko Jerusalemia m…®g…®a ghaze, me Jerusalemra iz…® ofa gamir dakozir vam…®ran God…®n ziam fam.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 8 ‚ÄúHesekia, n…® iz…® nan gumazir ekiam, Asirian atrivim ko akam ak…®righ. N…® ti 2,000plan m…®dorozir gumazir gavgavibar apight…®, nan atrivim 2,000plan hoziaba n…® danight…®, me dar apiagh m…®sogham. K…® fo, n…® uab…® gumazir kamagh…®n garitaba itir puvat…®.  
\v 9 Egha n…® kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, Isipian m…®dorozir gumaziba uan hoziaba ko karisba sara iz…® n…®n akuragh m…®sogham. Bar puvat…®gham, me izan kogham. N…® en m…®dorozir gumazibar tong…®n gumazir dapanir ziaba puvat…®zitam ab…®namin gavgaviba puvat…®gham.  
\v 10 N…® ti ghaze, k…® uab…® uan n…®ghn…®zim…®n iza n…®n kantri ko m…®sogha, a gas…®ghas…®si, a? Bar puvat…®. Ikiav…®ra Itir God uab…® na m…®kemez…®, k…® iza kantrin kam gas…®ghas…®si.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 11 Ez…® Eliakim ko, Sepna ko Joa akar kam baregha, kamagh…®n Asiriabar abuir gumazim m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® Aram…®n akam…®n e m…®k…®m, e a g…®fo. N…® Hibrun akam m…®k…®man mark…®. Puvat…®ght…®ma, gumazir nguibar ekiam…®n d…®vazir gavgavir m…®tiam gis…®n m…®tivighav itiba n…®n akam baregham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 12 Ez…® abuir gumazir kam kamagh…®n akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúNan gumazir ekiam pura akar kam…®n ia ko ian gumazir ekiam, a iarara m…®k…®masa na amadazir pu. Puvat…®. Gumazir d…®vazim gis…®n tuivighav itiba, me uaghan akar kam baragham. Guizbang…®ra, m…®dorozim otoght…®, e Jerusalem ek…®arugham, eght…® dughiar kuram bar ia batogham. Eght…® ia gumazir d…®vazim gis…®n tuivighav itiba, ia bar dagheba puvat…®gh…®va uan buaribar am…®va, uan m…®s…®zir pabar amam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 13 Ez…® Asirian abuir gumazim, d…®vazim gis…®n apiaghav itir gumazamizibar gara kamagh…®n pamtem…®n Hibrun akam…®n men d…®a me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa deraghv…®ra Asirian atrivir ekiam…®n akam baragh!  
\v 14 Atrivim kamagh…®n m…®gei, Ia Hesekia baraght…®, a ia gifaran mark…®. Hesekia ian akuraght…®, ia deragh ikian kogham.  
\v 15 Ia Hesekian apezeperir akaba baraghan mark…®, egh ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ik…® suam, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ian akuraght…®, e Asiriaba ia ab…®nigh Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam inighan kogham.  
\v 16 Ia Hesekian akam baragh ua na ko m…®soghs…® n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®. Ia derav…®ra dapiagh ik…®, egh ia uan mozir paba tu dar am…®va, wain…®n ikar…®zibar ov…®zibar am…®. Ia uan azenibar itir temer figh…®n ov…®ziba uan azenibar da inis…®, egh ia na ko akam ak…®righ na ateght…®ma, k…® ian nguibar ekiam iniam.  
\v 17 Eght…® ia deraghv…®ra ik…® mang…®t…®, k…® ia inigh mang…® kantrin igharazir ian kantrin m…®rara garim…®n ia at…®gham. Kantrin kam wain…®n azenir av…®riba iti. Egha a bret damuamin wit…®n azenir av…®riba iti. 
\p  
\v 18 ‚ÄúHesekia ia gifaragha ghaze, ‚ÄòIkiav…®ra Itir God, ian akuragh Asiriaba d…®kab…®ragham!‚Äô Ia Hesekia ateght…®ma a ia gifaran mark…®. Ia ti ghaze, kantrin igharazibar aseba men akurvasi, ez…® me Asiriaba e m…®sogha e ab…®ra, a? Bar puvat…®.  
\v 19 E ghua Hamat…®n nguibar ekiam ko Arpat…®n nguibar ekiam ko Sefarvaim ko m…®sozima, men aseba managh ikia, egha men akurazir puvat…®? Egha e ghua Samaria ko m…®sozima, Samarian aseba men akuragha e d…®kab…®raz, o? Bar puvat…®.  
\v 20 Kantrin kaba me aser av…®rav…®riba iti, ez…® e me ko m…®sosi. Ez…® men aseba men akuraz…®, me e m…®sogha e ab…®razir puvat…®. O Jerusalemia, ia manmaghsua n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ian akuraght…®, e ia m…®sogh ia ab…®raghan kogham? Bar puvat…®gham!‚Äù 
\p  
\v 21 Asirian gumazir dapanir kam me m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®, gumazir d…®vazir gavgavim…®n apiaghav itiba oregha fo, men Atrivim Hesekia faragha an akam ikarvagh bizitam…®n m…®k…®man men anogoroke. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me uan akabar kumigha an m…®g…®r…®g…®atam ikarazir puvat…®.  
\v 22 Ez…® Asirian abuir gumazim m…®kemezir m…®g…®r…®g…®aba, Eliakim, Sepna, ko Joa gamiz…® men naviba bar oseme. Ez…® me uan korotiaba ab…®agharigha ghua abuir gumazim…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®aba bar dar gun Hesekia m…®gei. 
\c 37  
\s1 Hesekia uan os…®mt…®zim…®n  // gun Aisaia m…®gei 
\r (2 Atriviba 19:1-17) 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® Judan Atrivim Hesekia Asirian atrivim…®n abuir gumazim…®n akam baregha, uan korotiaba ab…®agharigha buaber korotiaba aghuigha, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n ghu.  
\v 2 Egha atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n garir gumazim Eliakim ko, atrivim…®n ak…®nafariba osirir gumazim Sepna, ko ofa gamir gumazir ghuribar diaz…®, me izi. Ez…® a me amangiz…®, me Emos…®n otarim, Aisaian ganasa zui. Ez…® gumazir kaba, azirakar korotiaba aghuigha zui.  
\v 3 Me ghuava otivigha kamagh…®n Aisaia m…®gei, ‚ÄúAtrivim Hesekia ghaze, Kar os…®mt…®zir ekiaba ko aghums…®ziba otivir dughiam. Asiriaba d…®bovir m…®g…®r…®g…®ar av…®ribar e gami. E amizir navim asangiz…®m…®n m…®n ami, a borim batamin dughiam otoz…®, an a batamin gavgaviba puvat…®.  
\v 4 Asirian atrivim uan abuir gumazim amadaz…®, a iza d…®bovir akabar en God…®n Zurara Ikiav…®ra Itim m…®keme. E fo, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, an d…®bovir akaba baregha g…®fa, egh gumazir kamagh…®n amizim, God ivezir kuram a dan…®ngam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® en akuragh God ko m…®k…®mt…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, e varazira en akuraght…®, e ovengan kogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 5-6 Ez…® Aisaia Hesekian akam baregha, kamagh…®n gumazir an akam inigha izir kabav gei, ‚ÄúIa uamategh atrivim bagh mang…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam…®n gun a m…®kemegh. Ikiav…®ra Itir God ghaze, ‚ÄòN…® akar a nan tiraghtirazir kam, m…®gh…®gh a g…®n…®ghn…®gh atiatingan mark…®. A pura Asirian atrivim…®n ingangarir gumazir k…®nim, a m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam gami.  
\v 7 Ia oragh. K…® uan Duam…®n gavgavim…®n, Asirian atrivim damight…® an okam n…®ghn…®gham. Egh a m…®g…®r…®g…®ar k…®nim baregh pura uamategh ar…® uan kantrin mang…®gham. An Asirian kantrin ik…®v…®ra ik…®t…®, k…® gumazitabar amight…®, me a m…®sueght…® an aremegham.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\s1 Asiriaba ua Jerusalem  // gas…®ghas…®gha m…®gei 
\r (2 Atriviba 19:8-19) 
\p  
\v 8 Ez…® Asirian abuir gumazim kamagh…®n oraki, Atrivim Senakerip Lakis…®n nguibam ataki. Ez…® abuir gumazir kam d…®kavigha Jerusalem ategha ghua Libnan nguibam…®n otogha garima, an atrivim Lipnan nguibam…®n ikia Lipnabav sosi. Ez…® a ghuava atrivim bato. 
\p  
\v 9 Asiriaba m…®sogha itima, gumazir maba iza Atrivim Senakerip m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúItiopian Atrivim Tirhaka uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko iza n…® ko m…®soghasa.‚Äù Ez…® Senakerip Jerusalem iniasa n…®ghn…®si, kamagh…®n amiz…®, an ak…®nafarir mam osiriz…®, an abuir gumaziba a inigha Hesekia bagha ghu.  
\v 10 Senakerip kamagh…®n ak…®nafarim osiri, ‚ÄúHesekia, k…® fo, God…®n n…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim itim, a n…® m…®g…®a ghaze, k…® m…®sogh ia ab…®nigh Jerusalem inighan kogham. A n…® gifari. N…® bar an akam baraghan mark…®.  
\v 11 E Asirian atriviba, n…® uab…® en arazibagh fo, e kantrin igharazibar atriviba ko m…®sogha bar me gas…®ghas…®si. Egha n…® ti ghaze, k…® n…®n kantri kamagh…®ram a damighan kogham? Puvat…®, ia guizbang…®ra e gitaghan kogham.  
\v 12 Nan inazir afeziaba fom…®ra, Gosen…®n nguibam, Haran…®n nguibam, Resep…®n nguibam, ko Iden…®n gumazamizir Telasar…®n nguibam…®n itiba, me nguibar kabagh as…®ghas…®ki. Ez…® men aseba men akurazir puvat…®, ez…® me deragha ikezir puvat…®.  
\v 13 Ez…® nguibar kaba, Hamat, Arpat, Sefarvaim, Hena, ko Iva, men atriviba dat…®r…®gh…®n managh…®ra iti? Me itir puvat…®. E bar me m…®soaghar…®ghiz…® me ariaghire.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 14 Ez…® Atrivim Hesekia ak…®nafarir kam, abuir gumazir a inigha izeziba dama an suiragha an ganigha, a inigha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n ghu. Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n an onegha anet…®.  
\v 15-16 \x - \xo 37:15-16 \xt Ua Me Ini 25:22\x*Egha Hesekia kamagh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko m…®gei, ‚ÄúO Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, n…® Israelian God, n…® ensel…®n bar gavgavibagh afiragha bar p…®n uan atrivir dabirabim gaperaghav iti. Ez…® n…®n gavgavim ensel…®n bar gavgavibar gavgavim gafira. N…®rara, n…® guizbang…®ra God, n…® nguazir kam…®n kantribar gumazamiziba bar me gativagha men gari. N…®rara, overiam ko nguazim…®n ingari.  
\v 17 O Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…® deragh kuarim at…®gh nan m…®g…®r…®g…®aba baregh, egh derav…®ra bizir kurar e bativizir kabar gan. N…® God…®n Angam…®ra Itim. Ez…® Senakerip n…® d…®pova m…®kemezir akar kaba, n…® deragh da baregh dar gan.  
\v 18 O Ikiav…®ra Itir God, e kamagh…®n fogha g…®fa, Asirian atriviba kantriba bar dagh as…®ghasigha men nguaziba saram as…®ghas…®ki.  
\v 19 Egha atrivir kaba, kantrin kabar marvir guaba sarama as…®ghasigha da isa avim…®n da tue. Men marvir guar kaba, da guiz…®n godba puvat…®, me temeba ko dag…®aba isa uan dafaribar dar k…®ri. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Asiriaba bar mogh…®ra dagh as…®ghasigha, dagh apongez…® da isi.  
\v 20 O Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…® en God, n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n en akuragh Senakerip…®n dafarim…®n uam en inigh. Eght…® nguazir kam…®n kantribar gumazamiziba bar kamagh ganigh fogh suam, n…®rara n…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God.‚Äù 
