\v 1 Dughiar kam…®n, Asiriaba bar arazir kurabar Judabagh amima, Hesekia ar…®mariam inigha atam areme. Ez…® Emos…®n otarim Aisaia ghuava an ganigha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòN…®n ar…®mariam g…®vaghan kogham, a ik…®v…®ra ik…®t…® n…® ovegham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® gumazamizir n…®n d…®penim…®n itibav kemeght…®, me n…®n ingangariba bar dar amu dar k…®righ.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
