\v 7 \x - \xo 38:7 \xt 2 Atriviba 20:8\x*‚Äú‚Äâ‚ÄòK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® ababanitam n…® danight…®, n…® kamagh fogh suam, k…® damuasa akam ak…®righa g…®vazir bizim, k…® a damuam.  
\v 8 N…® gan! Ababanir kam kamak…®n, Atrivim Ahas fom…®ra ingarigha asarazir ad…®r…®ziam, ia an dughuazibar gara aruem…®n auaba medi. Aruem dat…®r…®gh…®n ghuaghiri, eght…® k…® a damight…®, a t…®m…®ra uamategh overiam…®n mang…®t…®, an angazangarim…®n dughuazim ad…®r…®ziam…®n 10plan ighuvibar p…®n uamategh ghuavanabogham.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù\f + \fr 38:8 \ft Judabar arazim kamagh…®n. Atrivim Ahas asarazir ad…®r…®ziam, a men klogh…®n m…®n iti. Aruem an garima, an dughuazim, ad…®r…®ziar ighuvibar gisira, ez…® me dughuazim gara fo, kar auan manam.\f* 
\p Ez…® aruem uaghira ad…®r…®ziam…®n dughuazim gamima, a zuam…®ra t…®m…®ra uamategha p…®n ghua ad…®r…®ziar ighuvir 10…®n p…®n itim…®n tu, a dat…®r…®gh…®n 10plan auan a faragha ikez…® mogh…®n iti. 
\p  
