\v 21 Aisaia faragha kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúAtrivim…®n ingangarir gumaziba, figh…®n ov…®zir me apuziz…® taba inigh, da m…®rm…®righ d…®patam darugh da munumigh da inigh iz…®, Hesekian okar gavgavim dukuaght…®, a ua deragham.‚Äù 
